 *
 */

Title;
ods noproctitle;
ods graphics / imagemap=on;

proc glm data=WORK.'MIGRAINE CLASSIFICATION'n;
	class Type;
	model Duration=Type;
	means Type / hovtest=levene welch plots=none;
	lsmeans Type / adjust=tukey pdiff alpha=.05;
	run;
quit;
